cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.DS

This paper deals with access control policies in computer networks, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR) and computer networks (cs.NI). The use of a permissioned blockchain implementation (Hyperledger Fabric) also suggests a possible fit with distributed computing (cs.DC) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the implementation and evaluation of an experimental prototype may also involve data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
